racide® cmitmit series of biocides and preservatives investments are under way to fully support this business including manufacturing warehousing and laboratory expansions to service dbsm biocides customers dalian biochem is an excellent partner for special materials company they are clearly a leading manufacturer of technologically advanced and high quality biocides and preservatives with a desire passion and wherewithal to penetrate markets on a global scale states michael dellicompagni chief operating officer of special materials company smc brings its market customer distribution and manufacturing expertise making dbsm biocides the new flexible alternative to the current market supply status quo xianwu liu chairman of dalian biochem comments in todays global economy i and my us partner smc would like to help our customers to succeed in what they are doing with our combined capabilities we are in a good position to satisfy the current needs of the us market june    new york ny  charlie neale appointed new oil  gas manager with special materials company we are pleased to announce charlie neale has joined special materials company as its new oil  gas manager in the north american region mr neale will be responsible for the management and support of key accounts and the sales strategy of smc oil  gas business and will be based in louisiana charlie neale is a qualified microbiologist and water treatment expert he holds a bachelor of science in microbiology from southeastern louisiana state university as well as graduate studies in aquatic toxicology and environmental management he has over  years experience in specialty chemicals predominantly in industrial water treatment applications waste remediation and most recently oil  gas applications charlie neale has worked for callaway chemicals  vulcan performance chemicals in the s and more recently with kemira as key account manager oil  gas in holden louisiana we are delighted that charlie has joined the smc team to strengthen our technical and sales expertise in both our oil  gas and water treatment business verticals with an emphasis on biocides and new business development as we build our organization we look for the best and the brightest and clearly charlie exemplifies these traits his reputation in the market speaks for itself said michael dellicompagni special materials company chief operating office coo december    new york ny  jeffrey m watson appointed new product manager for special materials company special materials company smc has appointed jeffrey m watson as a new company product manager with over  years of experience in the chemical industry he brings not only a wealth of knowledge to the position but he rounds out special materials company smc already strong and entrepreneurial product team according to adam feldman special materials company ceo our goal is to use all of our strengths creativity and energy to help and support not only our customers partners and suppliers to reach the goals and objectives but our employees too we know that our continuing success is built on every interaction that we have with all of them our reputation grows by doing this diligently and carefully and i am sure that jeff watsons contribution to the company will be very valuable jeff watson summarized why he joined special materials company smc by stating i am extremely excited to join special materials company and appreciate the opportunity to be part of such an enthusiastic organization smc has demonstrated significant growth for many years i strive to support smc and the goal of further growth the energy and entrepreneurial spirit is encouraging and i hope to bring my knowledge and skills to contribute to further success prior to joining special materials company smc jeff held key development and account managing positions at cognis corp arkema inc and rhodiasolvay october th   expansion of aryl phosphines and phosphinic acids production capacity smc has completed its latest capacity expansion of aryl phosphines and phosphinic acids at its yancheng jiangsu china joint venture plant the facility will increase production of benzene phosphinic acid bzpa aka phenylphosphonic acid as well as production of the phosphinate salts sodium benzene phosphinate nabzpa and potassium benzene phosphinate kbzpa our yancheng facility is an excellent base of operations to address the current markets needs aryl phosphorous derivatives find use as building blocks for a variety of niche industrial applications such as catalysts and intermediates in the fields of high performance polymers yarn production metal recovery corrosion protection in metalworking fluids dispersants and lubricity of hightemperature greases said kevin huber executive vice president of special materials company in addition to the new aryl phosphines expansion the yancheng site produces phosphorous based flame retardants september th   avancid® biocide earns us environmental protection agency registration for use in industrial water treatment and oilfield applications special materials company smc is pleased to announce that the us environmental protection agency epa has granted registration to the companys avancid® biocide product for use in water treatment and oilfield applications avancid® biocide is a seventy five percent solution of tetrakis hydroxymethyl phosphonium sulfate thps a widely used and highly effective chemistry for water treatment according to tom haack global business manager at special materials company avancid® biocide provides our customers with a more costeffective solution for mitigating problems associated with bacterial growth in industrial and oilfield water systems than has previously been available to them our company philosophy has always been to offer superior products with proven performances at a very competitive price and avancid® biocide delivers all that avancid® biocide is a fastacting microbiocide that controls troublesome bacteria and dissolves iron sulfide at low use levels it is stable and effective in high sulfide environments and is recognized for its benign environmental profile and rapid decomposition after discharge these properties make it a product of choice for oil recovery operations and industrial water treatment systems avancid® biocide is a registered trademark of special materials company september th   michael dellicompagni appointed new chief operating officer specialty materials company smc is pleased to announce the appointment of mr michael dellicompagni as its new chief operating officer coo mr dellicompagni who joins special materials company after more than  years with brenntag north america has commenced with smc in early september  mr dellicompagni was formerly the director of sales and sourcing for brenntag north america in this role he led brenntags north american sales and sourcing team comprised of presidents vice presidents and company executives in developing supply and sales strategies for key product lines commenting on the appointment of mr dellicompagni adam feldman smcs chief executive officer said a proven and effective leader michael possesses a diverse and extensive background including sales business development operations marketing ebusiness new business startup sourcing strategic relations and contract negotiations as we continue to grow we need to focus on providing strategic direction and operational support to smcs successful and growing specialty chemical business and establish more of a leadership and management structure to help us to do what we need to do in an efficient productive manner adam feldman continues by saying i am confident that in his new position as chief operating officer michael will continue to successfully identify opportunities from new and existing markets to further develop our specialty chemical niche products and services to allow special materials company to remain at the forefront of our industry mr dellicompagni chief operating officer of smc comments i am extremely excited and fortunate to join special materials company smc has grown to be the th largest chemical distributor in the united states and in the top  chemical distributors globally in addition to chemical distribution smc is also a very successful chemical producer their entrepreneurial spirit has been at the core of their success this is substantiated by the fact that adam feldman ceo of special materials company has recently been recognized by ernst and young ny as the  entrepreneur of the year as smcs tag line states providing a competitive advantage there is passion throughout the organization to be unique and to satisfy the customers needs in any way possible smcs approach to the market is quite distinctive and the caliber of people are best in class as i strive to provide leadership and structure i will not lose sight of the entrepreneurial spirit that has made smc the company it is today as chief operating officer i look forward to sharing my knowledge and experience across the company and supporting smc in its goal for further growth and success in the specialty chemical industry july th   special materials co smc makes the icis top  chemical distributors list  special materials co smc has made the icis top  chemical distributors list this year smc stands proudly no  of the top  and no in the north america region icis chemical business magazine ranked the companies by  sales reporting that special materials co had sales of  million that year we are thrilled to be ranked in the top  chemical distributors and its very gratifying to see our name listed among all these chemical industry leaders the credit goes to our expanding customer base and our dedicated employees worldwide said ceo adam feldman we are developing leading positions in many niche industrial products since our size and structure gives us the flexibility to grow and adapt to market needs much more quickly than other companies coupled with its local presence special mat